GERUND vs INFINITIVE                                                                    prepared by Uğur ARSLAN, @arslanuguur

---> Fillden isim yapma
INFINITIVE        --- to go
GERUND            --- going


                   GERUND                                                                       INFINITIVE    
                    
                V        Ving                                                               V      TO      V  
        -------------------------->                                                  -------|--------------|----->
                 action 1                                                                action 1       action 2
                 action 2


                   GERUND                                                                       INFINITIVE
            preposition + gerund                                                        noun/pronoun + infinitive
            --------------------                                                        -------------------------
